ivardefs.name: gender
ivardefs.desc: Administrative Gender - the gender that the contact person is considered to have for administration and record keeping purposes.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A name associated with the contact person.

ivardefs.name: organization
ivardefs.desc: Organization on behalf of which the contact is acting or for which the contact is working.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: The period during which this contact person or organization is valid to be contacted relating to this patient.

ivardefs.name: relationship_
ivardefs.desc: The nature of the relationship between the patient and the contact person.

ivardefs.name: telecom_
ivardefs.desc: A contact detail for the person, e.g. a telephone number or an email address.

properties.desc: A contact party (e.g. guardian, partner, friend) for the patient.
